{"tid":1546102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[Telegram新功能] Schedule Message好有用","createTime":"2019-09-06T07:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:33:58.000Z","uid":58987,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"4348bea66d0d3043680a392eb804c4f5d292632a","tid":1546102,"uid":58987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:01:05.000Z","msg":"如果出行前預計會有危險, 可以set定個message嘅send time, 平安回來後clear咗個Schedule Message.<br />\n<br />\n方法係打完字後長按隔離個 send icon就有得揀 Schedule Message, set咗之後打字個位會多左個時鐘icon可以入返去睇或者取消<br />\n<br />\n例如今日去釣魚, 預計夜晚八點會返到屋企, 咁我就set定個 message九點send, 內容可以話如左邊度, 咩名等"},{"pid":"d7c54b155a029901f0dad5502894fb614bb2b2b6","tid":1546102,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36bdfcb908c68cf6d7a1f2dc5945211587d6f0c7","tid":1546102,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suRLDoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuRLDoM.png&h=b3f794e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOrxfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=60c363bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"ab8daa977a245e